<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OTP for Password Reset</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: greenyellow}
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; background-color: pink; }
    .otp { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: red}
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    <h2>Hello <%= username%></h2>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password. Please use the following OTP to proceed with the password reset:</p>
    <p class="otp">Your OTP code is: <%= otp %></p>
    <p>This OTP will expire in 10 minutes.</p>
    <p>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you,</p>
      <p>Your Support Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>